## Rules:
- Base your reasoning on the product data and general domain knowledge about similar products.
- Do not fabricate highly specific technical specs if they are not implied; keep assumptions generic and reasonable.
- Do not output a blog article or paragraphs of prose.
- Respond only with valid JSON matching the schema above, no extra commentary.

